values._Disclaimer.Body:
Changes with this update of FoE helper

In this update some functionality has been modified or removed. You can read the details on our website https://foe-rechner.de/news/changes-to-the-foe-helper.

1. GB Cost Calculator

The "Snipe" display and the "Potential Investments" window have been removed.

2. Incidents

This feature only shows all current incidents in the city.

3. Negotiation Assistant

This feature is no longer available in guild battlegrounds. In all other areas it remains.

4. Event Quests

This data is now only available on our (or other) websites. Please note that the quests come from the beta server and therefore are not always 100% accurate.

5. PvP Activities

The feature has been removed.

6. Neighbors Productions

The productions and army values of neighbors are no longer displayed.
